Detailed Description

cvmx_gmx::_rx::_rx_inbnd

GMX_RX_INBND = RGMII InBand Link Status

Notes: These fields are only valid if the attached PHY is operating in RGMII mode and supports the optional in-band status (see section 3.4.1 of the RGMII specification, version 1.3 for more information).
